  "body": "Tilde not expanded:\r\n```console\r\n$ pwd\r\n/home/lightclient/go-ethereum\r\n\r\n$ ls ../scripts\r\nfile.js\r\n\r\n$ geth attach --jspath=~/scripts --preload=file.js http://localhost:8545\r\nFatal: Failed to start the JavaScript console: file.js: open ~/scripts/file.js: no such file or directory\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut absolute path works:\r\n```\r\n$ geth attach --jspath=/home/lightclient/scripts --preload=file.js http://localhost:8545\r\nWelcome to the Geth JavaScript console!\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\nLooks like `DocRoot` is not being expanded? https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/f19a679b09500e63b2fd134a4e829591174d9e48/cmd/geth/consolecmd.go#L90\r\n\r\nThen it's used here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/d8ff53dfb8a516f47db37dbc7fd7ad18a1e8a125/internal/jsre/jsre.go#L242\r\n\r\nedit: removed references to broken relative path since it was a user error :)",
